# Everything under pkg/ is generated by ../build-wasm.sh (cargo + wasm-bindgen).
# CI rebuilds these on every push; nothing here belongs in the repo.
# Keep this .gitignore committed so the pkg/ directory exists even in a fresh clone —
# build-wasm.sh writes into it, and mkdir -p is fine, but a committed marker keeps
# the intent visible.
*
!.gitignore
